# Test files export-ignore
tests/ export-ignore
*_test.* export-ignore
test_*.* export-ignore
**/test/ export-ignore
**/__tests__/ export-ignore

# Development files export-ignore
*.log export-ignore
*.tmp export-ignore
TODO.md export-ignore
NOTES.md export-ignore
scratch/ export-ignore
tmp/ export-ignore

# Linguist (GitHub language detection)
docs/** linguist-documentation
examples/** linguist-documentation
